name: #bouncingFRAME19
description:
Here is my frame for BouncingOBJKT24, a collaboration project with 24 artists organized by @jeremy_pires.
The shot was taken during the first BouncingBoy's space travel.

#bouncingOBJKT24 is a small testimony of the amazing #nftcommunity that #HEN has built and made possible. A BouncingOBJKT made of 24 frames from 24 HEN artists all gathered in 1 loop. Thanks to all those kind and talented people, we are the #24for24.
